text: Rosalba dissimilis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Belon in 1903. It is known from Argentina and Bolivia.BioLib.cz - Rosalba dissimilis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Apomecynini Category:Beetles described in 1903
title: Rosalba dissimilis
